Edit In Place provides inline editing of elements on a page using ajax.

Project Goals:
UX
Speed
Flexibility

Steps to accomplish:
Provide configuration on a per field instance basis to allow administrators to turn on 
	edit in place functionality.
On field display, if edit in place has been enable on that field, wrap the field in 
	a div with appropriate meta data and load widget and associated javascript onto page.
User activates the edit in place by clicking edit button which appears on hover.
User makes appropriate edits and then clicks save (or optionaly cancels).
Edit form is submitted to callback which builds up entity edit form and submits.
On success, the underlying markup is updated and widget disapears.
On failure, appriate error messages are displayed.
